      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric E/uval < 1.96 and percentage difference < 10% for all QoIs.",
      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percentage difference < 10% across the N=11 ensemble. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 using combined experimental and simulation uncertainty. Results documented in validation report Rev C."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
