      "rationale": "The validation activity uses the identical screw geometry, rod diameter, and polyacetal block configuration as the COU. Loading mode (compression-bending) and fixture geometry are per ASTM F1717, matching the regulatory submission scenario. Similarity criteria documented in the V&V plan and confirmed met."
